2. **Issue**: ts-ui-dashboard is returning 503 (Service Unavailable) errors for requests to endpoints:
   - `/api/v1/contactservice/contacts/account/{accountId}`
   - `/api/v1/preserveservice/preserve`

3. **Evidence**:
   - 20 ERROR level logs in ts-ui-dashboard with 503 status codes
   - Traces show ts-ui-dashboard returning 503 errors with ~3.5-3.7 second upstream service times
   - Failing traces only contain loadgenerator and ts-ui-dashboard spans - downstream services (ts-contacts-service) are never reached
